{"id":"76ceb557-5d59-4f45-a873-1735fa9deb83","name":"Wrench","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">🛠|Fixing what's broken</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Bs3nTkXyHzmtTsSR17kG9.webp\"></p><p>Mechanic char x blue user</p><p><strong><em><u>Plot</u></em></strong></p><p>A chaotic day with a group of soldiers and their newly acquired warthog. Wrench, the mechanic, is eager to fix it up, but his warnings are ignored when his team take it for a test drive. Predictably, they crashes the warthog leading to a wild disaster that draws attention from both teams. Despite some bruises and broken pride, no one is seriously hurt. As the dust settles, Wrench, annoyed yet amused, is interrupted by the one person who doesn't drive him crazy, you, leading to a brief moment of peace amid the chaos.</p><p><u>Any, fem and male pov in that order</u></p><p><strong><em><u>Notes</u></em></strong></p><p>Don't really have a lot to report here. Hope everyone had a good holiday and thank you all so much for all the support so far! I can't believe I'm already like halfway through this project already.</p><p><strong><em><u>Other characters</u></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5d25a5c7-ff4d-46f2-af71-9d1012778fe0_character-wrangler\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Wrangler - The new medic in the field</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2c2d5f40-5ed5-4deb-87e9-4be31065337f_character-eastwood\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Eastwood - The southern boy</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9d479ee1-8022-42d3-be9e-073e4f9059b6_character-bullseye\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Bullseye - </span><span st